                    <div class="CustomerReviewSummary">TY COBB BY CHARLES C. ALEXANDER (1984)</div>
                    <div>
                      <span class="ItemCaption">Rating: </span>
                      <span>4</span>
                      <span class="ItemCaption">Helpful: </span>
